    "description": "Pastel Putter is a simple mini golf game demo with a cel-shading inspired feel.<br><br>Putt your way through short little mini golf courses with the relaxing soundtrack in the background. Whether you want a casual game to play in long game queues, or simply want a relaxing way to pass the time Pastel Putter's chill vibe is perfect for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147340/extras/4c8919ae71047b54fa49e1eb60fd83c7.poster.avif?t=1666763354\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147340/extras/4c8919ae71047b54fa49e1eb60fd83c7.webm?t=1666763354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147340/extras/4c8919ae71047b54fa49e1eb60fd83c7.mp4?t=1666763354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Click and drag to line up your shot, then release to send the ball flying.<br>Don't launch it too hard or you might go flying off the edge!!!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147340/extras/3c17933fbdcf993648da681165f409d8.poster.avif?t=1666763354\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147340/extras/3c17933fbdcf993648da681165f409d8.webm?t=1666763354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147340/extras/3c17933fbdcf993648da681165f409d8.mp4?t=1666763354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play a single hole or a few dozen, easily jump in and out to of the game<br><br>created by a one person team with love!!",
